text: Shailendra Man Bajracharya (Nepali: शैलेन्द्र मान बज्राचार्य) is a Nepalese politician, belonging to the Hamro Nepali Party. He is currently serving as the member of the Bagmati Provincial Assembly. == References == Category:Living people Category:Nepalese politicians
title: Shailendra Man Bajracharya
